The paper deals with the problem of maximizing revenue in a multi-item auction with independent private distributions, which is a classic topic in game theory and mechanism design. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.GT (Game Theory). The paper also involves the analysis of dominant strategy and Bayesian implementations, which are related to decision theory and information theory, respectively. Therefore, cs.DS (Decision Theory and Game Theory), cs.EC (Economics and Computation), and cs.IT (Information Theory) are also likely categories. Finally, the paper uses mathematical formulas to derive exact solutions, which is related to optimization and machine learning. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a possible category.
